{
  "stem": "232.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a-- a whole mess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you couldn't make much noise because if the blockalteste was listening and hear there's a-- something going on, he came out and we get all beaten.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who was the blockalteste, do you remember?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My blockalteste happened to be a French guy, a Jewish guy, who was a-- who was a-- the blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He probably was in a different camp before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he must've been an organizer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was chosen as blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the one who got the soup in-- in the-- in the evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he is the one who got all the portion of breads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were cut.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They knew from one bread, a square bread, you can make four portions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, they were checked out from the oberkapo too that a portion should be OK.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what they did-- what they did do, we found out later, they cut the bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the middle, they cut a big trench away, pushed bread together, and then they made four pieces out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the blockalteste, of course, had always extra bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was giving it to his friends, if there were French people from his country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he give them the bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you could not exist in this camp without any help because the food was figured out for 100 to 120 calories.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the quarantine camp, you were not working hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you came from the outside, so you were-- you were still fed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Not as miserable as the other people, who were called muselmann, you know, who were long in the camps and they were so skinny.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if you don't organize some food, you couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was after four-- after four weeks, we graduated to the working camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
